stories.title: Naved shows class with 113
stories.summary:
Pakistan, known to be bad chasers, proved everyone wrong by
overhauling Sri Lanka's stiff 272 comfortably to earn a
morale-boosting win by seven wickets in the dress rehearsal
for Sunday's final of the Khaleej Times Trophy here Friday
before the

stories.title: Inzamam, Naveed Latif take Pakistan to victory
stories.summary: A courageous century from Naveed Latif and an antithetically sparkling hundred from Inzamam-ul-Haq shepherded Pakistan to a victory that will give them a massive boost when they take the field against Sri Lanka on Sunday
